Tynan is the owner of Tynan's Fishing Supplies in Port Piscarilius. He is found in his fishing shop due north-east off the docks. He is seen wearing a white apron and a green cap. He sells empty buckets, small and big fishing nets, fishing rods, harpoons, lobster pots, bait, and sandworms, which the latter is used to catch anglerfish.

At 30% Piscarilius favour and level 15 Hunter or above, players can aid him in collecting buckets of sandworms off the beach. Players will need a spade and empty buckets to perform this activity.

Treasure Trails[edit | edit source]

  • Tynan is the solution to the easy cryptic clue: Thanks, Grandma!
